      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) below 5% for NIH quantity of interest across three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three meshes (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.2M cells) were evaluated using Richardson extrapolation. GCI for NIH was 3.8% between medium and fine meshes. The 5.8M cell mesh was selected for production runs, meeting the Gradation 2 requirement."
