      "rationale": "FDA experimental data were collected under controlled laboratory conditions with traceable flow measurement (±2% accuracy) and tachometer-verified rotational speed (±0.5%). Boundary conditions in the CFD model were set to match reported mean experimental values. Achieved Gradation 3 due to comprehensive uncertainty documentation in the experimental dataset."
