      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry, which is the same device class as the COU. Operating conditions in validation (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) encompass the CPB operating envelope. Validation activities are directly relevant to the COU."
