      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; standard SST k-omega turbulence model selection with documented precedent is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on published precedent for centrifugal blood pump simulations. Formal model-form uncertainty assessment is not required at MRL 2. Accepted at Gradation 1."
